# operations-on-large-numbers
Example input data:
```
4
12345678901234567890+98765432109876543210
12345678901234567890*98765432109876543210
12345678901234567890-98765432109876543210
98765432109876543210/12345678901234567890
```
Expected output:
```
111111111011111111100
1219326311370217952237463801111263526900
-86419753208641975320
8
```
